Super Eagles midfielder Joe Aribo grabbed a brace for his Scottish side, Rangers as they walloped bottom side Hamilton 8-0 to maintain their undefeated run this season. Aribo’s goals came in the 19th and 36th minute. The win takes Steven Gerrard’s side’s winning streak to six matches and a total of twelve from fourteen matches. Rangers who have played two more matches than their Glasgow rivals showed why they are now the bookmakers’ favourites to end Celtic’s record-equalling run of nine straight league titles. <img class="aligncenter wp-image-1490067" src="https://i1.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Aribo-stats.jpeg?resize=600%2C600&#038;ssl=1" alt="" width="600" height="600" srcset="https://i1.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Aribo-stats.jpeg?w=1600&amp;ssl=1 1600w, https://i1.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Aribo-stats.jpeg?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i1.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Aribo-stats.jpeg?resize=1024%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i1.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Aribo-stats.jpeg?resize=107%2C107&amp;ssl=1 107w, https://i1.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Aribo-stats.jpeg?resize=768%2C768&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i1.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Aribo-stats.jpeg?resize=1536%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i1.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Aribo-stats.jpeg?resize=58%2C58&amp;ssl=1 58w, https://i1.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Aribo-stats.jpeg?resize=194%2C194&amp;ssl=1 194w, https://i1.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Aribo-stats.jpeg?resize=130%2C130&amp;ssl=1 130w, https://i1.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Aribo-stats.jpeg?w=1280&amp;ssl=1 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" data-recalc-dims="1" /> Rangers have improved tremendously since they were shocked by Hamilton during the latt